snippet.title: Army Men: Sarge's Heroes (PSX/N64) - Commercial
snippet.description:
Commercial from the late 1990s, or 2000. Recovered from VHS.

Cropped with Mpg2Cut2, and then "fixed" with MPEG Streamclip. Hopefully the quality is satisfactory.
